    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/2ba514047a7e00f6b3639ca97a50792b.avif?t=1769534717\" width=450 height=119 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/d118956aad2b42e68d4986b734337a72.webp?t=1769534717\" width=446 height=45 /></span><br>不同的房间均有各自<strong>独特的效果</strong>和对相邻房间的偏好。找到最优的安放方式，就能从对手手中夺得战术优势、释放自己建筑群的全部潜力。<strong>找到最佳位置将会带来无与伦比的满足感</strong>！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/bc5369909058b956ff363565fea1dcf0.poster.avif?t=1769534717\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/bc5369909058b956ff363565fea1dcf0.webm?t=1769534717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/bc5369909058b956ff363565fea1dcf0.mp4?t=1769534717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/aeeb40e61048c7999753ecadea18e4fa.webp?t=1769534717\" width=448 height=45 /></span><br>谁让你的对手非要把基地建得离你这么近呢……不如在他们的主控室旁边安放一个满是炸药的房间，给他们一个教训吧！又或者，<strong>你也可以直接安放一门大炮去轰他们</strong>？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/40a5dceffe31d0cbb0f9010a13a4451b.poster.avif?t=1769534717\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/40a5dceffe31d0cbb0f9010a13a4451b.webm?t=1769534717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/40a5dceffe31d0cbb0f9010a13a4451b.mp4?t=1769534717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/7e6b7db8701b7f8f809ef0d62b948b4f.webp?t=1769534717\" width=444 height=45 /></span><br>通过被动奖励来强化你的策略方针，活用各种<strong>独特的特殊能力</strong>来确保在比赛中占得先机！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/ceccafc8c0c1b87f372a154f0195fb29.poster.avif?t=1769534717\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/ceccafc8c0c1b87f372a154f0195fb29.webm?t=1769534717\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/ceccafc8c0c1b87f372a154f0195fb29.mp4?t=1769534717\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/20824b70e949bf93c5a288e60e90ffc0.webp?t=1769534717\" width=443 height=43 /></span><br>建造奢华的巢穴是获得邪恶首脑青睐的极佳方式，但有时你也可以选择摧毁你的对手们、或是成为最后一个能够继续建造的人。你可以通过<strong>战役模式</strong>来体验不同的游玩模式，也可以在<strong>自定义模式</strong>中根据你的喜好微调各种细节，甚至可以<strong>和你的Steam好友们一同游玩</strong>！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/466fb56a6533696e8b7194a1870fdefe.avif?t=1769534717\" width=600 height=278 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/31d4c2f909f99e9d124a6e59854aee10.webp?t=1769534717\" width=444 height=43 /></span><br>每名角色都有自己专属的加成，适应<strong>不同的游玩风格</strong>。来发现谁是你最喜欢的反派跟班吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650860/extras/43021658492913c0119642cdff48ca55.avif?t=1769534717\" width=600 height=600 /></span><br>如果您有任何关于游戏方面的问题或者需要我们的帮助，请发电子邮件联系我们：[<a href=\"mailto:contact@redbeakgames.com\">contact@redbeakgames.com</a>]",
